# Component Authoring Rules

- Every component implements `IComponent`: `id`, `pins[]`, `tick(dt)`, `reset()`.
- Declare a **pin manifest** as a static property listing all pins with direction and type.
- `tick(dt)` receives delta time in seconds. Must be deterministic.
- Source behavior from real spec sheets. Cite datasheet in a comment.
- No React/Next.js imports. Components are pure TypeScript.
